574
00:48:25,464 --> 00:48:27,193
<i>I don't remember your name.</i>

575
00:48:27,299 --> 00:48:29,961
<i>It was so long ago. Clerici, you said?</i>

576
00:48:30,068 --> 00:48:34,368
Yes. And you said to me...
