583
00:48:50,455 --> 00:48:52,946
And I'd like to see you, that's all.

584
00:48:53,959 --> 00:48:56,985
<i>Let's see.</i>
<i>Could you come over to my house?</i>

585
00:48:57,095 --> 00:48:59,063
Yes. When?

586
00:48:59,364 --> 00:49:02,891
<i>Today if you like, after lunch.</i>
<i>Come and have a coffee.</i>

587
00:49:03,001 --> 00:49:05,970
