623
00:52:39,084 --> 00:52:41,814
- Do you like it?
- Yes. It's so pretty.

624
00:52:41,920 --> 00:52:45,117
The station, the hotel, and now here.

625
00:52:47,859 --> 00:52:49,588
- Please.
- Thank you.

626
00:52:53,631 --> 00:52:56,896
If you like,
later I could show you a bit of the town.

627
00:52:57,268 --> 00:52:59,930
Really? And then
when you come to Italy,

628
00:53:00,038 --> 00:53:02,097
I can show you
around Rome, everything.

629
00:53:02,207 --> 00:53:04,198
The piazzas, the churches, the Forum...

630
00:53:04,309 --> 00:53:05,469
Yes.

