to do that.

676
00:55:52,644 --> 00:55:54,475
All these years,

677
00:55:54,579 --> 00:55:58,310
you know what remained
most firmly imprinted on my memory?

678
00:55:58,416 --> 00:55:59,747
Your voice.

679
00:56:01,886 --> 00:56:04,946
Imagine a great dungeon
in the shape of a cave.

680
00:56:05,790 --> 00:56:09,692
Inside, men who have
lived there since childhood,

681
00:56:10,595 --> 00:56:14,531
