shows his puppets.

686
00:56:32,250 --> 00:56:34,150
That was November '28.

687
00:56:36,487 --> 00:56:38,250
Yes, I remember.

688
00:56:41,492 --> 00:56:43,892
Now try and imagine some other men

689
00:56:44,829 --> 00:56:47,127
passing behind that little wall

690
00:56:47,966 --> 00:56:51,527
bearing statues
made of wood and stone.

691
00:56:52,403 --> 00:56:54,530
