a better gift than these memories.

693
00:56:58,977 --> 00:57:01,537
The enchained prisoners of Plato.

694
00:57:01,646 --> 00:57:03,773
And how they resemble us.

695
00:57:03,881 --> 00:57:06,714
- And what do they see?
- What do they see?

696
00:57:07,552 --> 00:57:11,352
You who come from Italy
should know from experience.

697
00:57:11,456 --> 00:57:13,788
They see only the shadows
the fire makes

698
00:57:13,891 --> 00:57:16,587
on the back of the cavern
that faces them.

699
00:57:16,694 --> 00:57:18,662
Shadows. The reflections of things.

700
00:57:18,763 --> 00:57:21,960
